// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - ComputerDiary 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P3781942678" "You search through the bookcase and find what appears to be Neville Hank's diary.  You skim through some of the entries:<br><br>'...screamed a lot.  I don't like it when they beg...'<br><br>'...ripped my costume... why are they so mean to me...'<br><br>'...how many of my friends have left me?'."
// Answer Text :
"P794816843" "Skip ahead"
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P1894350012" "'...was still praying for me as my playfriend went to sleep.  I just wanted to keep playing fun game with my new friend...'<br><br>'...heard someone in my little funplace this morning.  Woke up before they found me, so now I'm going to play hide-and-seek...'<br><br>'...new hidey-hidey should do the trick.  No one will find...'"
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P1146800551" "'...are they here?  Have they come back to play with me...'<br><br>'...of them!  ALL OF THEM! CALLING FOR...'<br><br>'...finding me.  Can't run fast enough from...'<br><br>'...gotta run gotta run gotta run they're everywhere all of them calling me calling me...'"
// Answer Text :
"P2977482088" "Skip to the end"
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P3241333091" "'...come back every day and call for me hiding hiding hiding from all of them calling for me why why what did I do what did I do I was just playing...'<br><br>'...keeps praying for me all the time STOP PRAYING STOP STOP STOP or I'll kill myself so you don't get me ever ever never ever...'<br><br>'...can't do it i cant do it too much blood my blood cantdoitandtheyllgetmenowhelpmehelpmeijustwantedfriends...'"
// Answer Text :
"P4177222812" "Find Neville and bring him to the ghosts..."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - Neville 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P1658168007" "They keep saying I've done bad things... I just wanted to play with them... I just wanted to play with my friends..."
// Answer Text :
"P1935413552" "Neville.  I'll be your friend."
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P469786483" "You'll be my friend?  All of my old friends are here and they say I did bad things and they scare me and they keep praying and they won't stop and they're hurting ME AND IT HURTS!"
// Answer Text :
"P3177692925" "I can make the pain go away, Neville."
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P3822914265" "I'm hurt... Hurt real bad.  I didn't have anyone to play with... And my friends kept praying and saying I was doing bad things.  So I used my toys on myself to make them go away BUT THEY DIDN'T GO AWAY!"
// Answer Text :
"P319788998" "Let's play together, okay Neville?"
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P3287654600" "You'll play with me?  WOW!!! I'm very, very happy now!  If you keep the bad friends away from me, I'll show you my toys!  And I'll show you how I make smiles!  Big, red smiles!!!<br><br>Maybe we can make smiles together? I'll give you one first, okay?"
// Answer Text :
"P2895903273" "Of course, Neville.  Just follow me, alright?  You'll be safe..."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1931147331" "You've come across a way to track down a sick and twisted perversion of what you can barely call a human being.  This revolting creature dares to put on the guise of those who watch over the innocent, but rather than protecting them... He brutally slaughters them instead?  And now your friend on the force suggests that you hand over your evidence so that he can be put through the mockery of a court system back in Paragon City?<br><br>No.<br><br>Neville Hanks will be given a trial... but unlike the one he'd be given in Paragon, this one will make him pay for his crimes against humanity."
// AcceptString :
"P1778695977" "Seek out 'The Slicer' and preside over his trial!"
// SendOffString :
"P2402527410" "You were able to triangulate the direction Hanks was travelling towards when he was injured.  It seems he's holed himself up in some abandoned warehouse nearby.  While he's still weak, now would be a good time to track him down and give him the trial he deserves before it's too late.  You wouldn't want him to die before he faces the justice he's managed to evade all this time."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3203218099" "Give 'The Slicer' a... fair... trial."
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P2583706796" "If you don't track down Neville Hanks before he recovers, he might manage to get away.  And if he does, all the rest of his victims' lives will be on your hands, not his."
// TaskTitle :
"P2661107818" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Guilt-Stricken Trail of Blood</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color slategray><i>Villain Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P447100665" "You can hear the sound of wailing and moaning coming from deeper inside the warehouse.  Quickly!  Get to The Slicer before he kills another victim!"
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1117664091" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Guilt-Stricken Trail of Blood</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color slategray><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>Neville Hank's reign of terror has come to an end.  In a final act of cowardice, he slit his own throat rather than listen to his ghostly tormenters.  In the end, he got a fair trial in which he pleaded 'Guilty'.  You acted as judge, his victims the jury, and Neville played the role of executioner.<br><br>Justice has been served."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3697958347" "...Neville... We come for you...<em t=3>...Your judgement comes...<em t=3>...Your sentence is an eternity of agony..."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3861953624" "...Leave this place, still-living...<em t=3>...It is too late for Neville Hanks..."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P856364347" ""
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P241560559" "Hank Neville's Diary"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P2969258277" "Hank Neville's diary that he keeps on his computer."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P1738482053" "Nevermind"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
