"P3522148545" "It's sickening just looking at this man.  Even now, he's still in his home-made Longbow costume... Covered in countless bloodstains."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2196608531" "No... Please... I just wanted to play with you..."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P307496365" "I... I never played with you...<em t=3>...maybe...<br><br>...the faces are all the same..."
// Script Variable SayOnRescue :
