// Script Variable CAPTOR_NAME :
"P447808053" "Tortured Soul"
// Script Variable CAPTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P4258511424" "...Neville...<em t=3>...you will scream for eternity..."
// Script Variable CAPTOR_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3256852339" "...you will not avert his suffering, {HeroName}..."
// Script Variable Greeting :
"P1875711363" "Th... Thank you."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P2194906627" "No... They're praying again!  STOP PRAYING!<em t=3>{HeroName}... Make them stop praying!  You said you would be my friend!"
