"P494441310" "Neville's last, and final, victim has returned from the grave to torment his soul.  Unfortunately, the ghost doesn't seem to be too picky about who it torments."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3710791325" "...Neville... Neville Hanks... Come to us... Come to us so that you can writhe in agony UNTIL THE END OF TIME!"
