// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_VigToVil_SL8-9_Task_02 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - Amuleteer 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P2681052456" "{HeroName}?  What are you doin... I mean... What a wonderful surprise!  Hey, didn't you just have a birthday? Here... Why don't you take this amulet as a birthday present!  Go ahead - put it on..."
// Answer Text :
"P2732191372" "Cut the bull, sister."
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P2606006445" "Whatever do you mean?  I'm completely sincere in my offer of that perfectly safe and enchanting amulet - enchanting in the 'good looking way', not the mind controlling way, of course.<br><br>Why are you looking at me like that?  You don't trust me?<br><br>Hmph.<br><br>Can't say I didn't try."
// Answer Text :
"P3037737872" "What do these amulets do?"
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P885471542" "Well, they give you every wish you've ever - OW! - okay okay! FINE!<br><br>They transfer the wearer's conciousness into a central nucleus, leaving their body in full control of our whims and desires.  While we're parading them around like cute marionnettes, their minds are in a cluttered communal... well, Hell, for lack of a better word.<br><br>We're not too sure what happens if the body dies without the mind being transferred back into it.  Or if the Nucleus were to be destroyed, for that matter.<br><br>This is all new technology.  We're still in the R&D phase, if you must know."
// Answer Text :
"P108803911" "How do I stop the Nucleus?"
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P1621482756" "Stop it?<br><br>Teeheehee...<br><br>You don't."
// Answer Text :
"P3898145311" "Close"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3667956420" "The Carnival of Shadows is well known for their cadre of mentally compelled clowns.  If this note is true, it seems they've found a way to increase their numbers of brainwashed goons by now aiming at the lowest common denominator - street trash.<br><br>This is as good an opportunity as any to clean up the streets, even in the Rogue Isles of all places.  You'll have to thank the Carnival later for picking up all the trash so that you can... dispose of it easily."
// AcceptString :
"P3075939019" "Track down the Amulet giver and take out the trash!"
// SendOffString :
"P3391898803" "The note goes on to say where the Carnival is handing out the amulets of Superpyrite.  Seems there's some head honcho putting people through some stupid little rituals, so that's probably the guy or gal you'll want to look for.  All you need to do is show up and clean house, maybe with a couple extra points for inventiveness while you're at it."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P4006580670" "Clean up the Carnival's trash!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P398899101" "If you keep waiting around all day, you'll lose your chance at taking out the Carnival of Shadows AND a whole host of street-trash.  Get to that warehouse pronto!"
// TaskTitle :
"P2266208951" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>The Superpyrite Amulet</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color slategray><i>Villain Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1879574750" "From the unmistakable gutteral curses coming from down the hall, it sounds like Mangle has taken the Carnival's bait and shown up for an amulet.  This day is turning out better and better!"
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P2478185361" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>The Superpyrite Amulet</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color slategray><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You had yourself a very productive day!<br><br>Not only were you able to take out a couple of gutterpunks like Mangle and Stardusk, you were able to stop the Carnival of Shadow's new scheme.  AND!!!  And you wiped out the minds of countless gutterpunks throughout the Rogue Isles!<br><br>Not really, of course.  You didn't believe that Carnival mistress for a moment.  All those thugs will likely wake up with, well, a headache or something."
// Script Variable ObjectiveUIText :
"P790066369" "Find the Grand Amuleteer and talk with her"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P886151376" "Mangle"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P4182634075" "Tell me one more time...<em t=3>Why are we working together to get these amulets instead of me just killing you and taking them all for myself?"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P603015567" "If {HeroName} showing up was part of your trap, I will bind your soul to the lowliest of my minions!"
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P3730695028" "As for you, {HeroName}... I'll bind yours to the seat of my pants."
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2580870842" "I'll let you think about where I'm going with that."
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P582586469" "STARDUSK! Get over here NOW, you pathetic excuse for a bloated, diseased heifer!"
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2800866057" "Those amulets are mine!  I'll melt down all that SUPER pyrite and buy the WHOLE WORLD!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P859822740" "No!  That was MY pyrite!  MINE..."
// Script Variable BOSS_KILLEDHERO_DIALOG :
"P1720076480" "HA!  The Superpyrite is all MINE!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - ScriptMangleDown 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Description :
"P2649093379" "Take out Mangle while you're here"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P2504070779" "Stardusk"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3368021958" "QUIT YOUR WHINING!  I found the Amuleteer and she's an easy -<em t=3>{HeroName}?  Oh, this just got interesting."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P940252308" "And by interesting, I mean 'Awwww crap'"
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P1803609819" "So, look... We don't have to fight, you know?"
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3317336756" "I hear things about you, {HeroName}.  You're really like one of us, you know?"
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P13139352" "Crap..."
// Script Variable BOSS_KILLEDHERO_DIALOG :
"P1453491422" "Hehe!  You're a bit of a wuss, you know that?"
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P48971806" "YES!  Thanks, {HeroName}!  Now all that Superpyrite is mine and I don't have to pay this schmuck!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - ScriptStarduskDown 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Description :
"P4048699468" "Take down Stardusk"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P2032281495" "The Grand Amuleteer"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P1895902432" "A high ranking member of the Carnival of Shadows, the 'Grand Amuleteer' is heading up this ruse to recruit new members.  And judging by her name, they're looking for really gullible people, at that."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P583748573" "What you'll do instead is die, {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P1991289508" "Really?  Did you think I would tell you all that without killing you afterwards?"
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2512862449" "Even if you could, destroying the Nucleus would likely destroy all the minds of those already affected.<em t=3>Even you wouldn't do something like that, {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3056255626" "Um... You wouldn't... Would you?"
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P3935541839" "Sisters!  Stop {HeroName} from getting to the Nucleus!"
// Script Variable BOSS_KILLEDHERO_DIALOG :
"P679805886" "Next time?  Don't talk to the bad guy for so long, got it?"

