"P1336575679" "With the destruction of the Nucleus, you feel a VERY fast headache come upon you all of a sudden.  It's like a million thoughts suddenly cried out... Nah... More like one of those bad stress headaches.  It's gone now."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
