"P1038117013" "Your blood smells tainted, interloper."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P2645541870" "Your body will not do for my purposes..."
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P980434399" "Therefore I will destroy you instead."
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P959977814" "Your only hope is to destroy the altars..."
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P1498271976" "But the price you would pay... HAHAHA..."
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P2411854517" "My hosts are legion..."

