"P890628734" "Polar Shift"
// Script Variable PET_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3788120005" "{HeroName}... You gotta save me!  I'll make it worth your while."
// Script Variable SayOnRescue :
"P4039914755" "Okay...  Now for that payment - um - I left my purse in my other costume."
