// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P2143579070" "Very well.  We tried to be reasonable.  Now you will all die... Painfully."
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P2542622282" "Ghoulish Delight"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P841801312" "Although this may look like Ghoulish Delight, in truth it's his brother, the heroic Ghost Twirler."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2695826531" "Hey, girls!  I got away from them AND have the subsonic devices!<em t=3>This was a lot more fun than I thought it was going to be!"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P79525735" "{HeroName}?  Why are you looking at me like that?<em t=3>Don't you know I'm an evil, demonic demon undead guy?"
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P446229924" "Why are you... Oh no... You found out?"
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P1285051272" "Look, I owe my brother a favor, okay?<br><br>He's getting his appendix out and my mom's final wish before she died was to help my brother if he was ever in the hospital."
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2843482803" "What was I supposed to do, {HeroName}?  Risk having my mom come back from the dead?  And she would, too - I've seen her do it A LOT!"

