// Dialog :
"P1006528347" "The lesson didn't turn out exactly as you had planned.  And sadly, it was Flamespout's final lesson..."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - ReturnSuccess 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// RandomFameString :
"P72968560" "I've heard some things about that {HeroName} over there... And, well, they kinda scare me."
